Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.15,Princess Connect - Top,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư Karyl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.65,Princess Connect - Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Có cả thịt nữa đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.16,Princess Connect - Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Không thấy đâu hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.17,Princess Connect - Top,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Bé Karyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:14.07,Princess Connect - Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Karyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.25,Princess Connect - Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Karyl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.65,Princess Connect - Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư Karyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.74,Princess Connect - Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư Karyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:28.28,Princess Connect - Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Mình là... Hiệp Sĩ Công Chúa của người đó...
