Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.19,Princess Connect - Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Không thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:38.79,Princess Connect - Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Thử tìm đằng kia xem sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.93,Princess Connect - Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Đừng có hét to toáng lên nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.27,Princess Connect - Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Xấu hổ lắm biết không.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:55.07,Princess Connect - Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Chúc mừng em trở về, bé Karyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.39,Princess Connect - Italics,Karyl,0,0,0,,Vì ai đó ư...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.38,Princess Connect - Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Tôi về rồi đây.
